Title: Kim Possible
Writer: Josh A. Cagan (script), Josh A. Cagan, Mark McCorkle (characters), Mark McCorkle (script), Mark McCorkle, Robert Schooley (characters), Robert Schooley (script), Robert Schooley
Actors: Sadie Stanley, Sean Giambrone, Ciara Riley Wilson, Todd Stashwick
Plot: Heroes Kim and Ron face the problems of starting high school as freshmen when their team gets an addition. Every hero needs a villain and one's just been sprung from prison. Will Kim save the world again or will high school bog her down?
